  "experiment_name": "q215_tiny_reg_detach",
  "description": "FALSIFICATION: Tiny energy_reg (1e-10) + detach_epos. Tests whether a negligible reg can arrest q214 explosion (E\u21929e13) without suppressing pred_norm like q212 (reg=0.01 \u2192 pred\u21920). At E=447k: reg_grad=2e-10*447k=9e-5 (negligible). At E=9e13: reg_grad=0.18 (arrests explosion). If pred_norm reaches ~19.4 and val MSE\u21920.0097, the Goldilocks window exists. If not, energy-value contrastive is dead.",
